I asked @trueearther if he had the video of the pilot filming two suns while flying his plane and he sent me the first three videos... this fuckin guy hoards all the gravy I swear. If you looked in his fridge I’m sure all you would see is gravy. I bet he even has some stored for next year in his freezer. I don’t even want to know what his gravy boat collection looks like. 

-don’t mind the gay Star Wars picture. But even Star Wars, among all the lies shows us some truth. 

The third angel sounded his trumpet, and a great star, blazing like a torch, fell from the sky on a third of the rivers and on the springs of water
